iee","tag-israelites-banu-israeel","tag-knowledge-al-ilm","tag-manners-adab","tag-messengers-al-rusul","tag-narrating","tag-nation-ummah","tag-obligations-faraid","tag-people-of-the-book-ahl-kitab","tag-prayer-al-salat","tag-prophets-anbiya","tag-scriptures-kutub"],"aioseo_notices":[],"jetpack_featured_media_url":"","jetpack_shortlink":"https:\/\/wp.me\/p95VHY-1YF","jetpack_sharing_enabled":true,"jetpack-related-posts":[{"id":7591,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2012\/10\/04\/israiliyat-hadith-share-one-ayah\/","url_meta":{"origin":7605,"position":0},"title":"Hadith on Ayat: Narrate traditions from me, even a single verse","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"October 4, 2012","format":false,"excerpt":"Abdullah ibn Amr reported: The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cConvey from me, even a single verse. Narrate from the children of Israel, for there is no blame in it. Whoever deliberately lies about me, let him take his seat in Hellfire.\u201d Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 al-Bukha\u0304ri\u0304 3461 Grade:\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":26118,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2018\/03\/26\/women-adab-masjid\/","url_meta":{"origin":7605,"position":1},"title":"Hadith on Mosques: Women having proper etiquette in the mosque","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"March 26, 2018","format":false,"excerpt":"'Amrah bint Abdur Rahman reported: Aisha, may Allah be pleased with her, said, \u201cWere the Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, to see what women are now doing, he would have prevented them from attending the mosque, just as the women of the children of Israel were\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/sin-al-ithm\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":2901,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2012\/04\/16\/bidah-innovation-jews-christians\/","url_meta":{"origin":7605,"position":2},"title":"Hadith on Bid&#8217;ah: Muslims make same mistakes as previous nations","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"April 16, 2012","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Sa\u2019id al-Khudri reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cYou will surely follow the path of those before you, step by step and inch by inch. If they entered a lizard hole, you would follow.\u201d We said, \u201cO Messenger of Allah, do you mean\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":10296,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2012\/12\/14\/seventy-three-sects-sahaba\/","url_meta":{"origin":7605,"position":3},"title":"Hadith on Sects: Only followers of Sunnah and Sahaba enter Paradise","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"December 14, 2012","format":false,"excerpt":"Abdullah ibn Amr reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cWhat comes over my nation will surely be what came over the children of Israel, step by step, such that if one of them fornicated with his mother, someone from my nation would do the\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/faith-iman\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":1941,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2012\/02\/09\/difference-opinion\/","url_meta":{"origin":7605,"position":4},"title":"Hadith on Ikhtilaf: Companions interpret the Prophet&#8217;s order differently","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"February 9, 2012","format":false,"excerpt":"Abdullah ibn Umar reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, made an announcement on the day he returned from the Confederates, saying, \"No one will pray his noon prayer unless he is among the tribe of Qurayzah.\" Some people feared that the time for prayer would\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":17436,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2014\/01\/01\/prophet-recite-quran-nawm\/","url_meta":{"origin":7605,"position":5},"title":"Hadith on Quran: The Prophet recites Quran before sleep","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"January 1, 2014","format":false,"excerpt":"Aisha reported: The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, would not sleep in his bed until he has recited Surat Bani Isra\u2019il and Al-Zumar. Source: Sunan al-Tirmidhi\u0304 2920 Grade: Sahih (authentic) according to Al-Albani \u0639\u0646 \u0639\u064e\u0627\u0626\u0650\u0634\u064e\u0629 \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e\u062a\u0652 \u0643\u064e\u0627\u0646\u064e \u0627\u0644\u0646\u0651\u064e\u0628\u0650\u064a\u0651\u064f \u0635\u064e\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0649 \u0627\u0644\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0647\u064f \u0639\u064e\u0644\u064e\u064a\u0652\u0647\u0650 \u0648\u064e\u0633\u064e\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0645\u064e \u0644\u064e\u0627 \u064a\u064e\u0646\u064e\u0627\u0645\u064f \u0639\u064e\u0